msgid ""
"Sit down for serious laughs with Bourree Lam, Nothing Personal’s Executive Editor, and Ben Collins, CEO of The Onion. While many publishers are experimenting with AI-generated or AI-assisted "
"content, The Onion is doubling down on human-written satire."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.a8bae6ba-0c68-40a7-89d3-c7e0440c4de0"
msgid ""
"Ben discussed the outlet’s beautifully inefficient editorial process in creating America’s funniest news items. The Onion has revived its print edition and built a loyal subscriber base. He’ll also "
"discuss why the work of The Onion is more important than ever in the landscape of corporate news."
msgstr ""

